Xml: <xs:simpleContent>	<xs:extension base="xs:string">		<xs:attribute name="substitution" type="yes-no"/>		<xs:attribute name="alternate" type="yes-no"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="print-style"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="placement"/>	</xs:extension></xs:simpleContent>
<xs:simpleContent>	<xs:extension base="octave">		<xs:attribute name="number" type="xs:positiveInteger" use="required"/>		<xs:attribute name="cancel" type="yes-no"/>	</xs:extension></xs:simpleContent>

<xs:simpleContent>	<xs:extension base="positive-integer-or-empty">		<xs:attribute name="type" type="start-stop" use="required"/>		<xs:attribute name="slashes" type="xs:positiveInteger"/>	</xs:extension></xs:simpleContent>

<xs:simpleContent>	<xs:extension base="xs:string">		<xs:attribute name="number" type="ending-number" use="required"/>		<xs:attribute name="type" type="start-stop-discontinue" use="required"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="print-object"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="print-style"/>		<xs:attribute name="end-length" type="tenths"/>		<xs:attribute name="text-x" type="tenths"/>		<xs:attribute name="text-y" type="tenths"/>	</xs:extension></xs:simpleContent>

<xs:simpleContent>	<xs:extension base="kind-value">		<xs:attribute name="use-symbols" type="yes-no"/>		<xs:attribute name="text" type="xs:token"/>		<xs:attribute name="stack-degrees" type="yes-no"/>		<xs:attribute name="parentheses-degrees" type="yes-no"/>		<xs:attribute name="bracket-degrees" type="yes-no"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="print-style"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="halign"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="valign"/>	</xs:extension></xs:simpleContent>

<xs:simpleContent>	<xs:extension base="xs:string">		<xs:attribute name="type" type="start-stop-single" use="required"/>		<xs:attribute name="number" type="number-level" default="1"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="print-object"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="print-style"/>		<xs:attributeGroup ref="placement"/>	</xs:extension></xs:simpleContent>
